DTSTAMP:20260317T131510Z
DTSTART:20260325T080500Z
DTEND:20260325T081000Z
SUMMARY:Keynote: The CRA and What it Means for Open Source Communities - Greg Kroah-Hartman\, Linux Kernel Maintainer & Fellow\, The Linux Foundation
DESCRIPTION:The CRA is about to go into affect for manufacturers in the EU in a mere few months. &nbsp\;This short talk will go into the latest information from the EU CRA Expert Group as to how the law will affect the open source community and the companies who integrate open source into their products.
CATEGORIES:KEYNOTE SESSIONS
LOCATION:Hall 12\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
