SUMMARY:🚨 Contribfest: Crossplane Contribfest - Jared Watts & Nic Cope\, Upbound
DESCRIPTION:Join the Crossplane maintainer team for this interactive session focusing on high bandwidth collaboration where we will drive contributions to the finish line together. This session will take an “office hours” type of approach and is intended for an audience that is already familiar with Crossplane and has some hands-on experience within its broad ecosystem. If you have a design\, issue\, or pull request that you are excited about (maybe you’ve already started working on it even!) and want to make a difference by collaborating directly with the maintainer team\, then this session is for you. Let’s ship some code together!
