SUMMARY:Sponsored Demo: Testing 2\,000 Container Images on EKS: Inside Chainguard’s Agentic Factory
DESCRIPTION:Chainguard and AWS have partnered to bring Chainguard's catalog of zero-CVE container images directly to the EKS Marketplace\, but the 2\,000+ images available as EKS add-ons are just the tip of the iceberg. Shipping secure\, zero-CVE container images is hard. Continuously shipping a colossal catalog is a different problem entirely.\n\nDustin Kirkland (SVP Engineering\, Chainguard) will take you inside Chainguard Factory 2.0\, powered by DriftlessAF\, an open source agentic reconciliation framework built on the same reconciliation loop pattern that makes Kubernetes resilient. Instead of brittle\, clock-aligned pipelines\, DriftlessAF uses AI-powered bots that relentlessly compare desired state (zero CVEs\, latest packages) against actual state\, and reconcile the difference\, and reconcile the difference automatically.\n\nHe'll share the honest story of what it takes to validate an ever-increasing image catalog against EKS: the automation that exists today\, the gaps that remain\, and how agentic AI is increasingly closing them. A candid look at what continuous delivery of secure open source at scale actually looks like in production.\n \n\n**In order to facilitate networking and business relationships at the event\, you may choose to visit a third party’s booth or access sponsored content. You are never required to visit third party booths or to access sponsored content. When visiting a booth or participating in sponsored activities\, the third party will receive some of your registration data. This data includes your first name\, last name\, title\, company\, address\, email\, standard demographics questions (i.e. job function\, industry)\, and details about the sponsored content or resources you interacted with. If you choose to interact with a booth or access sponsored content\, you are explicitly consenting to receipt and use of such data by the third-party recipients\, which will be subject to their own privacy policies.**
CATEGORIES:SOLUTIONS SHOWCASE
LOCATION:Hall 1-5 | Solutions Showcase\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:3217f102c81dcb15687a573e37ad3b17
URL:http://kccnceu2026.sched.com/event/3217f102c81dcb15687a573e37ad3b17
